{"about_the_game":"One Chance is an addictive game that puts your reaction time to the test. The objective of the game is to drive along a path filled with moving obstacles without colliding into any of them. The game is unlimited, allowing you to spend as much time as you want trying to increase your own record. With a simple yet challenging gameplay, One Chance keeps you on edge as you navigate through a series of obstacles that require quick thinking and precision. You must think fast and act quickly to avoid the obstacles and keep your finger moving. The game's scoring system encourages you to keep pushing yourself to improve your performance. The more obstacles you successfully navigate, the higher your score will be. With each attempt, you can strive to beat your own record and climb up the leaderboard.<br>One Chance is designed to be easy to pick up but difficult to master, providing endless hours of fun and challenge. With no time limit and no end to the game, you can keep playing and improving your score for as long as you like.<br>Do you have what it takes to navigate through the obstacles and increase your score in One Chance? Play now and find out!<br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlimited route<br></li><li>Unforeseen obstacles<br></li><li>Simple and addictive interface</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1716491768","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862040/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1716491768","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1716491768","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862040/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1716491768","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"